topic.title: CISCO IOS 12.3 source code leak
topic.body:
yo, has anybody got the CISCO IOS 12.3 source code leak that happened in 2004?
IOS-11.2-8 is out there in many places (like here https://github.com/lololosys/cisco_ios_research/tree/master/IOS%20Source%20Code/IOS-11.2-8/)
but the newer one (from 2004) is very rare.
Can anyone link me the the leak from 2004 or anything newer?
Thanks in advance my dudes
